if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n變相冇得轉頁要係咁掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d344415d7e9a74744b19564a9d4c6b15378321fd","tid":17383,"uid":21732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以加番HKG+嗰個睇圖功能<br />\n姐係啲留言就算冇用[img] post ，睇圖功能都識自己開<br />\n<br />\n有時好多條link 慢慢禁入去好慢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實依家有整<br />\n不過有 d link 可能無 url scheme ( 姐係 http:// )<br />\n所以分析唔到，將來試下改善<br />\n<br />\n或者你提供下有問題既 post 俾我地<br />\n會比較方便研究</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 五點都做緊野 你地係咪唔洗訓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/14950/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/14950/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n依個post 啲相好似有http:// <br />\n<br />\n同埋點解冇得直接copy一個post 既link 同人share （定我唔識禁）<br />\n<br />\n上面有人話qoute 會太長 有冇得set 到係用家自定顯示幾層qoute"},{"pid":"5cccef500f9f260109866a0ad659fb0d6f0e9835","tid":17383,"uid":21732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d先叫聽意見，叫真心覆<br />\n早洩mode : thx</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早洩果啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsorry<br />\n明白<br />\n正一死狗mode 屌都廢事"},{"pid":"d5b84b3c389e6cb29c00500e56928ea2459e4206","tid":17383,"uid":49861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:07:19.000Z","msg":"點解可以快到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351cdd1630c0d8113033abc44b58ef41cdc46cf8","tid":17383,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:22:08.000Z","msg":"1.) 用緊iphone6 ios 8.1 每次回覆同發帖之後都會彈app，重開app之後係會見到出左文，但發件夾就唔會見到，要去回帶搵<br />\n<br />\n2.) ios 開完個app，無kill到，隔幾個鐘之後再開，之前係吹水台嘅，再開都會係吹水台，但上最高之後向下拉等佢refresh，成版都唔識轉，要拉左邊果行出黎再禁多次吹水台先轉到<br />\n<br />\n3.) 有時㩒入post會唔知點解load唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/082204_01ee3adc20022e49cf433ded141e2cbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F082204_01ee3adc20022e49cf433ded141e2cbc.jpg&h=85d1c3e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0595cd09c660c6f0de27e95aba515069d73dab2c","tid":17383,"uid":10481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"望遠巴打<br />\n<br />\n主頁向下拉 refresh 呢度， 可唔可以改 拉小小就refresh 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。大機手指短 有d辛苦"},{"pid":"fc8fc6c43cce33b43d06c377688bfd7fd2eb887b","tid":17383,"uid":1807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"望遠 我知你仲係度<br />\n如果你唔覆再開post標題有admin就召喚到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用嘅時候成日禁到右手邊果三粒點<br />\n下面就會彈野出黎<br />\n可唔可搬左個位佢"},{"pid":"da4b6c89e392a7e9d3b1bbb7ba7a0f323cb77ca7","tid":17383,"uid":3,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:45:04.000Z","msg":"上面既意見同問題回報我都有睇哂<br />\n會幫大家處理下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1852a3705b25276ade6fa4ed46b6fe6ade7ffa10","tid":17383,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 長噤功能(取消回帶,留名 etc.) 彈出選單改成方便d既 好似hkg+咁彈波波出黎都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望幾位大佬可以考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下個版本會加 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5點半啦大佬<br />\n可唔可以唔好咁痴線啊<br />\n訓啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br 